profile:
We are committed to providing an excellent service across Toronto, GTA and nearby regions. In our decade of experience, we have learned that you can get your appliance, HVAC, electrical and plumbing issues repaired quickly, effectively, and relatively inexpensively. Our specialty is to provide quick solutions to all your appliance, plumbing, HVAC and electrical repairs and to achieve the highest possible customer satisfaction from our services. Our punctual and friendly staff will always provide budget-friendly repairs.

WHY DO OUR CUSTOMERS LOVE US?
"Slow is smooth, smooth is fast." This is our motto because we take exceptional care in locating your appliance and plumbing faults to have them fixed within the shortest possible period. We encourage our customers to watch us as we perform the repair and to ask as many questions as possible while we are on site. This will ensure the best service on the market because you will be educated on all of your appliances at no extra cost.
Man With a Wrench always provides an above and beyond service because we do not simply tackle the problem at hand. We also find its underlying cause. Most importantly, we provide our customers with education as to how to prevent such problems from occurring in the future. Our budget-friendly repairs are second to none and we will provide you with quick solutions to all of your appliance repair needs. Our goal is to delight you with our service. If you don’t go shouting from the rooftops how happy you are with your service following a work order, we will be very disappointed, for our business runs on word-of-mouth referrals and we strive to ensure you’re happy enough to tell your friends about our service

WHAT APPLIANCE REPAIR SERVICES DO WE OFFER?
We will repair any major appliance and any major brand for: 
- Refrigerators repair 
- Stove repair 
- Oven repair 
- Washing Machine repair 
- Dryer repair 
- Dishwasher repair 
- Microwave repair

We repair all makes and models, we even repair Miele appliances! Other brands we service regularly: Frigidaire, Simmons, Samsung, LG, GE, Kenmore, Thermadore, Whirlpool, Kenmore, Maytag, Moffat, Dacor, Fisher and Paykel, Thermador, Electrolux, Bosch, Sub Zero, Amana, Jenn-Air, Wolf, AEG, Magic Chef, Viking, Blomberg, Admiral, Westing House, Ariston, MagicChef, Inglis - IF THE Brand is not on the list WE CAN DO IT (we just missed it).

WHAT PLUMBING SERVICES DO WE OFFER?
- Toilet repair 
- Drain cleaning
- Plumbing repairs
- New installations (sinks, toilets, showers) 
- Water pumps
- Water heaters
- Frozen pipes
- Re-piping
- Burst Pipes
- Leak Detection 
- Inspections

We service Toronto and all surrounding areas. That includes: Toronto, Whitby, Oshawa, Pickering, Scarborough, Markham, Aurora, Newmarket, Brampton, Bradford, Oakville, Mississauga, Etobicoke, North York, East York, GTA, Burlington, Barrie, Innisfil and all of the cities that surround the cities listed


We look forward to servicing your appliance and plumbing HVAC and electrical repair needs!

profile:
With well over hundreds of household appliances shipped daily, fully stocked showroom, and a mega warehouse to keep our inventory fully stocked, we are currently one of the largest retail suppliers of household appliance throughout Canada. Our success has been built on a simple principle: take care of every customer as if they are a member of our family.   

Besides for having a local appliance showroom in Toronto, we are the only independent appliance
e-commerce dealer in Canada fully authorized to sell household appliances online and supply you with cost saving rebates that our competitors can't offer you. This assures that you enjoy the peace of mind knowing our products are fully backed by the full support of the manufacturer.  That coupled with our own extensive customer service, assures you that your satisfaction is of our utmost importance. 

Customers always ask us how we can afford to offer such low pricing.  The answer is, because of the sheer volume of our sales, and the mass volume we buy, we are able to negotiate rock-bottom pricing with our distributors, which we can then pass on to you, the consumer.

 

Remember, everything you buy from us is brand new and manufactured sealed. Every item we sell comes with the model# and serial# on the unit and can be verified with the manufacture for its authentication.

 If you need appliances for your first home, your dream home or the lake home, we have the latest products in all styles and price ranges. Whether you’re interested in cooking products, refrigerators, washers, dryers, dishwashers, food disposers, and barbeques, we have you covered. We promise you a truly unique shopping experience from your own home!  When you shop at our store, you’re supported by a group of dedicated professionals who are serious about selling appliances. If you need a quote, specifications, product information or just ideas, we’re at your service. Our mission is to make your buying experience unique and hassle-free. When you do business with our company you have a relationship with individuals, not a big corporation. As our company continues to grow, we’re going to keep it that way.
products: We ONLY sell brand new, factory-sealed products. We never sell used, refurbished, or out-of-box units. All of our products come with a full 1 year manufacturer's warranty. We are 100% Canadian owned and operated and are a fully authorized Canadian appliance dealer.

services: How to Donate to ReStore: Simply call the ReStore to determine if your donation item is for drop off, pick up, or appraisal. Once we have your donated items in the ReStores, you will be mailed out a donation receipt for the assessed value of the item(s).
